==體能鍛鍊與身心健康==
規律的運動是維持健康的關鍵之一，而且對於保持健康[[體重|體重]]、[[消化系統|消化系統]]、[[骨密度|骨密度]]、[[肌肉|肌肉]]能力、[[關節|關節]]自由活動、[[生理|生理功能]]、降低往後需要面臨[[手術|手術]]治療的機率以及強化[[免疫系統|免疫系統]]有著顯著的貢獻。迄今許多文獻表明：規律的運動可能增加一個人的[[預期壽命|預期壽命]]及整體的[[生活品質|生活品質]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Gremeaux|first1=V|last2=Gayda|first2=M|last3=Lepers|first3=R|last4=Sosner|first4=P|last5=Juneau|first5=M |last6=Nigam|first6=A |title=Exercise and longevity.|journal=Maturitas|date=December 2012|volume=73|issue=4 |pages=312–7|pmid=23063021 |doi=10.1016/j.maturitas.2012.09.012 }}</ref>。

有規律運動且其運動強度大達到大約中{{NoteTag|中度約指運動過程中感到稍微喘，不太能聊天。}}、中強、強的程度的人，相對於沒有規律運動習慣的人，可能有較低的死亡率、較低的[[老化|老化]]（氧化）速度及減少體內[[發炎|發炎]]的機率<ref>{{cite journal |title=Physical Activity and Health |url = https://books.google.com/?id=WZZPc1FmL7QC&pg=PA3&dq=+United+States.+Department+of+Health.+Physical+activity+and+health:+a+report+of+the+Surgeon+General.+diane+Publishing,+1996.#v=onepage&q=United%20States.%20Department%20of%20Health.%20Physical%20activity%20and%20health%3A%20a%20report%20of%20the%20Surgeon%20General.%20diane%20Publishing%2C%201996.&f=false |journal=United States Department of Health |doi=|pmid= |date= |access-date= |isbn=9781428927940|author1=Department Of Health And Human Services |first1=United States|year=1996}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Woods|first=Jeffrey A.|last2=Wilund|first2=Kenneth R.|last3=Martin|first3=Stephen A.|last4=Kistler|first4=Brandon M.|date=2011-10-29|title=Exercise, Inflammation and Aging|journal=Aging and Disease|volume=3|issue=1|pages=130–140|issn=2152-5250|pmc=3320801|pmid=22500274 }}</ref>。

